---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="New England Crust is in the process of joining several affiliate programs. Learn how we handle affiliate links and commissions."
>
  <section class="container-page py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">• Disclosure</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl text-balance md:text-5xl">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-timber-200/70">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert mt-8 max-w-none
                  prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:text-timber-50
                  prose-a:text-glow-200 hover:prose-a:text-glow-300">

        <p>
          New England Crust is in the process of joining several affiliate programs. When those
          partnerships become active, some posts on this site will contain affiliate links —
          meaning if you click one and buy something, we may earn a small commission at no
          additional cost to you. This page will be updated with the specific programs we're part
          of once they're approved.
        </p>

        <h2>Our standards, regardless</h2>
        <p>
          Every product we write about is something we have personally cooked on, used, or would
          genuinely buy ourselves. Affiliate relationships, when they exist, do not influence what
          we recommend or what we say about it. If we wouldn't recommend something to a friend on
          the deck, we don't write about it here.
        </p>

        <h2>When links are live</h2>
        <p>
          We won't label every affiliate link individually — this page will cover them site-wide,
          as the FTC allows. Cookie windows vary by program (typically 24 hours for Amazon, 30
          days for most others). The price you pay is identical whether you use our link or go
          directly to the retailer.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this disclosure, or anything else on the site? Reach us through the
          <a href="/about/">About page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
